16/12/2002
ROME, Italy -- Croatian President Stipe Mesic will meet with Pope John Paul II and Vatican state secretary Cardinal Angelo Sodano on Monday (16 December). 
Later, Mesic will speak during a ceremony presenting the Croatian Christmas tree at St Peter's Square. 
Last week, the Croatian government delivered and decorated the largest tree at the square, as a present to the Pope. 
(HINA, HRT, BBC - 15/12/02)
